msgid ""
"<1.so>You see those <2.se_co>cannons<3.re_co>?<4.pa> I'll draw their\n"
"fire.<5.pa>\n"
"\n"
"While I'm doing that, use your\n"
"<6.se_co>bomb arrows <7.re_co>to <8.se_co>destroy the "
"cannons<9.re_co>.<10.se_co><11.pa><12.re_co>\n"
"Got it so far?\n"
"If you need to withdraw for a bit, just\n"
"<13.se_co>spread your cloth<14.re_co> and float <15.se_co>straight "
"up<16.re_co>\n"
"in the updraft for a while.\n"
"I'll take that as a sign that we need to\n"
"regroup.\n"
"\n"
"Don't bother aiming for anything covered\n"
"by <17.se_co>Medoh's barrier<18.re_co>. It's impenetrable.<19.pa>\n"
"\n"
"And whatever you do, don't get close\n"
"enough to touch it.\n"
"\n"
